-- Kvitova, Ferrer Advance to Fourth Round at French Open Tennis
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-06-02T11:18:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-02/kvitova-ferrer-advance-to-fourth-round-at-french-open-tennis.html
Wimbledon champion Petra Kvitova and
 David Ferrer  advanced to the fourth round of tennis’s French
Open.  Kvitova, the No. 4 seed from the Czech Republic, beat
Russia’s Nina Bratchivoka 6-2, 6-4, 6-1 at Roland Garros in
Paris. Sixth-seeded Ferrer of Spain defeated 27th-seeded Russian
Mikhail Youzhny 6-0, 6-2, 6-2.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  